Entrypoint directory: 
    Only run .initgitconfig script from here.

Entry script:
    ./.setup:       setup PATH and other env variables
                    invoke full installation and configuration script
    ./.softclean:   soft cleans the setup, no package will be removed
                    only the user defined environment will be cleaned.

Arguments:
    --type=[min|default|dev|full]
        min < default < dev < full
    --log-target=[term|file]
        term: terminal - this is default
        file: logs and errors to .logs and .errors respectively
    --custom-setup=[server-minimal]
        server-minimal: used for minimal installation, mainly for servers
